[Student "S"]
{SOUTH has a powerhouse and knows she will reach a slam somewhere. When NORTH 
supports the \Ss, it seems she has found her spot.

Blackwood tells her that NORTH has two Aces. 
She can see there are 12 tricks available and decides to take a chance that 
NORTH will have a thirteenth trick somewhere among his opening hand points.

She bids 7NT.}

